    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/86d788322d497b16bde068912a232c81.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/86d788322d497b16bde068912a232c81.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>踏上史诗冒险之旅！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好你的装备并决定：你会独自迎接这个挑战，还是与朋友并肩作战？选择权在你手中，这段旅程充满了兴奋与危险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=608 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/1e7684acb54a20f71dfa5637d7110049.mp4?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择你的道路</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演战士、弓箭手或法师，击败试图阻挡你的怪物。每个职业都提供独特的技能和游戏风格，选择最适合你的角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/9a0be8697bd5c8487badc024a175e264.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/9a0be8697bd5c8487badc024a175e264.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>进化与提升</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中获得经验，并在天赋树中解锁强大的升级。访问铁匠铺强化你的装备。成长的可能性是无穷无尽的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>留下你的印记</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的成就不会被忽视！与其他勇敢的冒险者竞争荣耀并比较表现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/069cb6f2750e16a5b1af5bcdce5bb8de.poster.avif?t=1749758786\" width=609 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120050/extras/069cb6f2750e16a5b1af5bcdce5bb8de.webm?t=1749758786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要错过这个机会！将游戏添加到你的愿望清单，并关注我们的每周更新，里面充满了新的挑战、功能和惊喜。这段旅程才刚刚开始，我们迫不及待地想看到你会走到哪里！</p>",
